org.hazelwire.modules
Class ModulePackage

java.lang.Object
  org.hazelwire.modules.ModulePackage

public class ModulePackage
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents the module package i.e. a set of modules that belong together. This can be used for packaging modules from the same wargame for instance.
